		<item>
			<title>Svemirske letjelice</title>
			<link>https://localhost/lzmk/e-leks/priroda-i-tehnika/553-svemirske-letjelice</link>
			<guid isPermaLink="true">https://localhost/lzmk/e-leks/priroda-i-tehnika/553-svemirske-letjelice</guid>
			<description><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://enciklopedija.hr/Natuknica.aspx?ID=36201" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Svemirske letjelice</a></strong></span> namijenjene su letu izvan Zemljine atmosfere, to jest u Zemljinoj orbiti, Sunčevu sustavu ili dalje u svemiru. Automatske svemirske letjelice nemaju posadu i namijenjene su obavljanju različitih znanstvenih i istraživačkih zadaća. Razlikuju se umjetni sateliti (gibaju se u orbiti oko <span style="color: #0000ff;"><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://enciklopedija.hr/Natuknica.aspx?ID=67110" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Zemlje</a></span> ili drugih svemirskih tijela) i međuplanetarne letjelice (gibaju se putanjom među udaljenijim svemirskim tijelima). <strong><span style="color: #8b2323;"><a style="color: #8b2323;" href="https://enciklopedija.hr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Hrvatska enciklopedija</a></span></strong> predstavlja nove članke o svemirskim letjelicama <strong><em><span style="color: #0000ff;"><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://enciklopedija.hr/Natuknica.aspx?ID=70880" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Pioneer</a></span></em></strong>,<strong><em> <span style="color: #0000ff;"><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://enciklopedija.hr/Natuknica.aspx?ID=70878" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Voyager 1</a></span></em></strong>, <strong><em><span style="color: #0000ff;"><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://enciklopedija.hr/Natuknica.aspx?ID=70879" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Voyager 2</a></span></em></strong>, <span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong><em><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://enciklopedija.hr/Natuknica.aspx?ID=70877" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Galileo</a></em></strong></span>,<span style="color: #0000ff;"><em><strong><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://enciklopedija.hr/Natuknica.aspx?ID=70876" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"> Cassini-Huygens</a></strong></em></span> i <span style="color: #0000ff;"><strong><em><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://enciklopedija.hr/Natuknica.aspx?ID=70881" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">New Horizons</a></em></strong></span>.</span></p>
<p class="feed-readmore"><a target="_blank" href="https://localhost/lzmk/e-leks/priroda-i-tehnika/553-svemirske-letjelice">Opširnije...</a></p>]]></description>
